<% content_for :exhibition do %>
  <div class="articleContainer">
    <div class="spacer">
      <div class="gridlayout">
        <article class="row">
          <div class="column col1-1">
            <div class="gridSpacer">
              <h1><%= image_tag 'projectlodge-light.png', :alt => '.projectlodge',:class => 'projectlodgeLogo' %>
                SAG 2012 Summer</h1>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="column col1-2">
            <div class="gridSpacer">
              <p>This will be our 5th gathering and the 2nd as an official association.</p>
              <p> Like the previous gathering the day will have two sections. The first is the general assembly for our members, after that the public program will begin.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="column col1-2">
            <div class="gridSpacer">
              <p> There will be several keynotes by interesting people. The various projects will be demonstrated, and you are invited to lend a hand right away. After that we can enjoy some short talks and we'll end the day socializing with drinks.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
      <div class="break"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
<% end %>

